				```

		calculationItem PQ =
				
				VAR vCM =
				    CALCULATE (
				        MAX ( 'D_Calendar_Filter'[Quarter Index] ),
				        ALLSELECTED ( 'D_Calendar_Filter' )
				    )
				VAR vResult =
				    CALCULATE (
				        SELECTEDMEASURE (),
